### Android原生组件
##### PopupWindow
  ```java
    PopupWindow popupWindow = new PopupWindow(content);
    popupWindow.setWidth(200);
    popupWindow.setHeight(200);
    popupWindow.setContentView(view);
    popupWindow.showAsDropDown(view, 40, 40);
  ```


##### ListViewAdapter
  ```java
  notifyDataSetChanged()
  ```
